Introduction

L5ST is a seven-member boy group under Macaroni Media. They made their debut on September 5, 2024, with their digital single “Only One.”

The group was officially revealed with a tweet featuring their logo on August 1, 2024. On August 17, it was officially announced that “Only One” would mark their debut. Seogyeom and Donggyu were revealed as members, but unfortunately, Eun had left the group by August 27.

On October 18, 2024 they announced their official fandom name and meaning.
"LOVE", the highest level of "love" It means “greatest love” and “most beloved”. It contains the meaning that L5ST (Lost) and their fans, LOV3ST (Lovelyz), give each other the greatest love and grow together.
